    "There are two main sides in this system as shown in Fig. 4: (i) the Child Side, and (ii) the Parent Side.",
    "Fig. 3 Emotion Detection Assistant (EDA) application",
    "To improve the performance of the algorithm to classify the input image efficiently, the proposed algorithm contains an autoencoder for feature extraction and feature selection Fig. 5.",
    "Autoencoder is a type of unsupervised neural network that attempts to make a compressed representation of the input data.",
    "The design of the autoencoder restricts the architecture to a bottleneck from which it can reconstruct the image."
